quests.desc: Hey, thanks for coming over to the TextWorld today, there is something I need you to do for me. First step, make an effort to venture west. Okay, and then, go to the west. And then, make an effort to travel south. After that, try to go to the east. Once you get through with that, attempt to go to the south. And then, attempt to travel east. And then, attempt to travel north. And then, attempt to move east. And then, pick up the worm from the shelf in the attic. And then, deposit the worm on the floor of the attic. Alright, thanks!

objective: Who's got a virtual machine and is about to play through an fast paced round of TextWorld? You do! Here is your task for today. First thing I need you to do is to move west. And then, head west. Okay, and then, move south. After that, venture east. With that accomplished, make an attempt to take a trip south. With that over with, go to the east. If you can finish that, go to the north. Then, attempt to head east. After that, recover the worm from the shelf inside the attic. Then, ditch the worm on the floor of the attic. Got that? Good!
